name: Middlefield Real Estate Dividend ETF
longDescription: The investment objectives of Middlefield Real Estate Dividend ETF formerly Middlefield REIT INDEXPLUS ETF are to i provide holders with stable monthly cash distributions, and ii enhanced long term total return through capital appreciation. The Fund Real Estate investment portfolio through an investment strategy that focuses primarily on investing in dividend paying securities of global issuers operating in, or that derive a significant portion of their revenue or earnings from, products or services related to the real estate and related industries.
